      "raw_text": "Percy Powell, of the Powell-San-\ntexyZynpany. returned today from\nWashington city, where he went as\nmember OF the Spokane commit\ntee to urge the passage of the\nlong haul, short haul\" bill in con,\ngress.\n\n\nMr.. Powell said that he saw 81\ncongressman and nearly as many\nsenators. and feels very much en-\ncouraged and thinks that the hill\nhas fair chance to go through\nboth houses of congress. He found\na strong sentiment in favor of the\nbill among the statesmen from the\nmiddle west and mountain states.\nMr.. Powell Is further very much\nencouraged over the prospect OF a\nFavorable decision by the interstate\ncommerce commission, which will\npnss on, the Spokane rate case be-\ntween now and June 10."
    }
